name: SKCloudServiceSetupOptionsKey
desc: Keys used to specify the types of setup options for a cloud service.

items.name: init(rawValue: String)
items.desc: Initializes a cloud service setup options key based on the provided raw value.

items.name: static let action: SKCloudServiceSetupOptionsKey
items.desc: A key that specifies the action for a setup entry point.

items.name: struct SKCloudServiceSetupAction
items.desc: A string used to specify the type of setup action to offer for a cloud service.

items.name: static let iTunesItemIdentifier: SKCloudServiceSetupOptionsKey
items.desc: A key that specifies the iTunes Store item that the user is trying to access through the service.

items.name: static let affiliateToken: SKCloudServiceSetupOptionsKey
items.desc: A key that specifies the iTunes Store affiliate token.

items.name: static let campaignToken: SKCloudServiceSetupOptionsKey
items.desc: A key that specifies the iTunes Store affiliate campaign token.

items.name: static let messageIdentifier: SKCloudServiceSetupOptionsKey
items.desc: A key that is used to select the main message presented to the user for this setup view.

items.name: struct SKCloudServiceSetupMessageIdentifier
items.desc: Identifiers for the available messages the setup view can present to the user.
